2000001.name: How will you fare against my blade?

2000003.name: One day I'll surpass my father!

2000004.name: I want to fight stronger opponents!

2000011.name: Lava was defeated? You expect me to believe that?

2000012.name: Get out of my way! My fight is with Lava!

2000013.name: Darn! I guess I didn't have what it takes!

2000022.name: You're not bad. You've piqued my interest.

2000023.name: To face a strong opponent is every warrior's dream.

2000024.name: How interesting! Show me more of what you've got!

2000031.name: I've no time to play around with you.

2000032.name: You might be difficult to deal with.

2000034.name: Looks like you're more than just talk.

2000041.name: It seems you aren't just a simple soldier.

2000043.name: Grafl! Pay attention! This one's quite capable!

2000051.name: Who's this? You're a strange one, aren't ya?

2000054.name: Let us show you our joint attack!

2000061.name: How odd...my blade is reacting to you.

2000062.name: How could such a warrior exist?

2000063.name: Allow me to show you my special move! Aurora!!

2000064.name: Allow me to see the burning fire in your heart!

2000065.name: My blade is like the fire of hades!

2000075.name: Even gods don't have the right to destroy people!

2000076.name: No giving up! I've still got some fight in me!

2000082.name: Have some Phoenix breast for all your hard work!

2000083.name: Let me cook something up for you!

2000084.name: Hold on! It's not ready yet!

2000085.name: The main dish is almost ready!

2000092.name: What is a god? Who is truly evil!?

2000093.name: I'm the thief who's going to steal your lives!

2000101.name: Let me fix your weapons for you!

2000102.name: Darn it! There's just no end to it!

2000103.name: Hey, hero! Are you using my weapons properly?

2000111.name: I'll burn everything, even the gods!

2000112.name: I can hear them. Wings! Come to your hero!

2000114.name: Let me show you the power of the black flame!

2000115.name: I'm defeated... Looks like I won't be seeing him now...

2000122.name: My life belongs to the empire!

2000124.name: My army will not be defeated so easily! Forward march!

2000132.name: To the one who noticed me...

2000133.name: I will take you with me!

2000134.name: I like it here! Away with you!

2000143.name: Check out these wings! I feel invincible!

2000148.name: This is the power of his wings!

2000149.name: Bring it on! I've still got a lot left!

2000181.name: I won't leave until I've accomplished my objective.

2000182.name: I'll show you Drevas' true power.

2000185.name: I guess I haven't matured enough.

2000191.name: I haven't seen you around here before.

2000192.name: I won't forgive you for what you did to Falma!

2000193.name: You dare defy those you have no chance of beating?

2000194.name: Falma! Time to show our true power!

2000202.name: I won't be done in by a youngster!

2000212.name: I won't make the same mistake again!

2000221.name: Youngster, what is it that you fight for?

2000222.name: The path to your dreams is full of hardship.

2000223.name: Can you go on, knowing the Demon Pike's curse?

2000224.name: Focus your will and free the World Tree.

2000241.name: I won't forgive any who cause harm to this forest.

2000242.name: A massive power is asleep just ahead.

2000244.name: Do not involve us in your quarrel!

2000261.name: Do you know the true identity of the Demon Pike?

2000262.name: When the World Tree awakens so will the forest.

2000263.name: I must protect the peace of the forest!

2000264.name: The person inside of me is excited.

2000265.name: It is impossible to deny the passage of time.

2000266.name: I recognize you as one cursed by the Demon Pike.

2000272.name: Still not enough... I need more...

2000273.name: Allow me to absorb your energy!

2000282.name: Who are you who disturbs my slumber?

2000283.name: Be not reckless, ye who is cursed by the Demon Pike.

2000284.name: My family, allow me to heal your wounds.

2000285.name: What is it you desire, Demon Pike!

2000286.name: The time has come for me to reveal myself again.

2000287.name: You have freed me from my seal!

2000288.name: I offer my power to your Demon Pike!

2000291.name: I fight to protect those I care for!

2000292.name: My bow is the strongest around!

2000293.name: I musn't lose! I can't let them down!

2000302.name: Fool! I'm going to end you!

2000303.name: What are you going on about!?

2000311.name: Your journey ends here! I'm not letting you through!

2000322.name: This battlefield just isn't enough for me!

2000323.name: There it is! The adrenaline of the battlefield!

2000331.name: Worry not, Drevas. We will not lose.

2000332.name: I won't forgive any who harm the God Tree.

2000335.name: Nngh... Drevas has begun to erode...

2000341.name: I once again grant my power to ye who released me.

2000342.name: The curse of the Demon Pike has only just begun.

2000343.name: I wonder how many times I will come back to this world.

2000353.name: My body has become one with Drevas.

2000357.name: It's hopeless for us at this rate!

2000358.name: Nngh, I feel like...I'm going to pass out...

2000359.name: Even after I'm gone, Drevas will still remain.

2000372.name: Take this! Can you handle my thunder?

2000373.name: Outta my way! Or I'll bash you all to bits!

2000374.name: Huh. You're not as weak as I thought.

2000375.name: Tsk! I'm just not in the mood today.

2000384.name: Why you so strong? I no understand...

2000391.name: This my territory. You. Get out!

2000393.name: Me hate you. You. Go away!

2000401.name: Grr! What's this, a snack for me?

2000402.name: Taking my heads won't be easy!

2000411.name: This lady... The things she can do with a sword!

2000412.name: I guess brute force does have its limits...

2000414.name: Step aside! I have bigger fish to fry!

2000421.name: Test your steel against my shining blades!

2000422.name: You there! You're in the way!

2000423.name: I have no mercy for those who harm the frail!

2000424.name: Defeat isn't an option when I fight for my people!

2000425.name: Ahh! I guess I need more training...

2000432.name: Hehe, you're pretty tough! But I'm not done with you yet!

2000433.name: You're wrong if you think I've shown you all my power!

2000434.name: Why are you staring at me like that?

2000435.name: I'm gonna get a lot stronger than this!

2000442.name: Let me show you my secret alchemy.

2000443.name: We need to cooperate if we're going to reach our goal, everyone!

2000444.name: The findings of my research? Those are a secret!

2000451.name: He he he, let's try to get along, everybody!

2000452.name: Wh-Who raises their hand to a pretty girl?

2000453.name: Attacking a p-pretty girl like that? Unforgivable!

2000454.name: A-Attacking your elder?! Have you no respect?

2000461.name: How did I end up on this journey? Is my training that lacking?

2000462.name: Burdened with these amateurs... I suppose this is another phase of my training.

2000463.name: I guess I have really strayed so far from my fencing days in La Veda...

2000475.name: Whoa... Didn't think people outside were this tough.

2000481.name: I'll take it from here! (R-Run away!)

2000482.name: I'm not done yet! (This one is way too tough!)

2000483.name: I'll show you what I'm really made of! (I'm done for!)

2000484.name: Ugh... I can't do this on my own!

2000485.name: Y-You haven't seen the last of Nemia, dodo!

2000491.name: Go back to where you came from! No swords allowed here!

2000492.name: Stop wasting my time, or I'll knock you into oblivion!

2000493.name: Hmph. Maybe you're not as weak as I thought!

2000494.name: There are guys this strong on the outside? This could get interesting!

2000502.name: Hear me roar and kneel before me!

2000504.name: Think your weapons can harm my flesh?!

2000505.name: You fool! You are the prey, not me!

2000506.name: Your blade is mighty, after all!

2000511.name: Here we go, Grafl! I'm counting on you, old friend!

2000513.name: Grafl! You won't get away with this, you fiend!

2000521.name: Gods?! Who cares? I'll shoot them all down!

2000522.name: Here comes cover fire, you scum!

2000523.name: Falma! My pistol will avenge you!

2000531.name: First, to test the enemy's skills...

2000532.name: We must at least let the common folk go...

2000535.name: Hmm, individual strength will certainly be needed at this point in the battle.

2000536.name: Even if you win this one battle...

2000537.name: I'll buy time for the common folk to escape!

2000541.name: How about I debone you like a fish?

2000551.name: I don't have time for the likes of you!

2000552.name: What are these little bugs squirming before me?

2000553.name: Your only advantage is your numbers!

2000555.name: Sheesh! This isn't going as I planned...

2000557.name: I won't let you down, Emilia!

2000561.name: I will crush the army of the gods!

2000562.name: Defeat isn't in my army's vocabulary!

2000565.name: You're an idiot to be respected!

2000566.name: You have no idea how to use your power!

2000567.name: You fool! So this is your limit...

2000568.name: Gah! I need more! More power!

2000573.name: The greatest idiot swordsman on earth is me!

2000574.name: I am Holy Thunder Eze! Remember my name!

2000575.name: Wow! Can you feel that energy flowing!?

2000577.name: You don't care what's about to happen to you?!

2000578.name: I'll zap you all into bits!

2000579.name: Super Thunder Crush, I command you!

2000580.name: Well, how did you like that?!

2000581.name: I haven't had enough fun yet!

2000582.name: Thunder Sword Batootha! Lend me your strength!

2000583.name: You haven't seen half of what the greatest idiot can do!

2000584.name: Blow their eardrums out with your deafening roar, Batootha!

2000592.name: It'll be a pain going home.

2000632.name: Some weirdo is in the way!

2000641.name: Go away! This ship is mine!

2000642.name: You're all bark and no bite!

2000643.name: How dare you make me angry?!

2000645.name: Get away you piece of trash!

2000651.name: Yo ho! Give up yer ship!

2000652.name: I won't let ye capture me!

2000683.name: Atro, the enemy is too weak.

2000694.name: I still have a ways to go.

2000701.name: I leave myself in your care!

2000702.name: This is fun! It's game on!

2000712.name: I will keep you at bay!

2000724.name: I'll give my life if I must!

2000732.name: The power of the gods is...

2000733.name: I must make this power mine!

2000754.name: It is time to use my power.

2000764.name: I shall show you my burden!

2000774.name: Good job! But you won't win!

2000781.name: You found me? Fight me then.

2000782.name: This won't be easy, will it?

2000802.name: His power has no reach here.

2000822.name: The real me is over here.

2000831.name: Can I try a piece of you?

2000834.name: You're as nice as I thought.

2000835.name: No! It's not enough for me!

2000842.name: We have no reason to fight!

2000855.name: Logan, I got good data. Heh.

2000871.name: Am I really of any use here?

2000873.name: I can only rely on myself.

2000874.name: In the end, I'm all alone.

2000903.name: I'll stop you here and now.

2000911.name: Gods? Stay out of my way!

2000912.name: This is my lance of revenge!

2000913.name: I use the armor of the gods!

2000922.name: Bare witness to my new form!

2000930.name: Take this hit full of anger!

2000941.name: Get out of my way, you!

2000954.name: Don't go easy on me, please!

2001026.name: I will not lose to you!

2001032.name: I don't care for your title!

2001036.name: I won't lose to him again!

2001051.name: You won't do as you please!

2001071.name: I can do it! Watch me!

2001083.name: My life might be at stake...

2001084.name: My pride is on the line!

2001103.name: Dad, trust me on this one!

2001127.name: Urias! I can still do this!

2001138.name: I won't give in! I'm needed!

2001140.name: Face the last of my power!

2001151.name: The God Army has made it here too?!

2001154.name: I'm sorry to have gotten you involved...

2001161.name: Don't worry, pretty lady! I'll escort you!

2001162.name: Hey! Are you okay, pretty lady?!

2001171.name: You dare lay your hand on a lady?!

2001172.name: No! I must not fail in my duty to protect others!

2001173.name: Friend! Leave this to me and focus on stirring the ship!

2001181.name: You want my help? Hmph. Are you up for a test?

2001182.name: You don't underestimate your enemies, do you?

2001183.name: Well then. One strike will decide everything!

2001184.name: You're weak! Don't forget to prepare against attacks!

2001192.name: So, you're trying your best now. Good job.

2001193.name: Wow, you're better than I thought.

2001194.name: What burdens do you carry on your shoulders?

2001201.name: How dare you treat Lady Edea in such a manner!!

2001203.name: Lady Edea! Don't place your trust in that person!

2001204.name: Ngh... I couldn't prove my strength, but--!

2001211.name: Loch, let's train before our big battle tomorrow!

2001212.name: Loch, if you don't hit your target, Edea will get mad!

2001213.name: Nice job! Guess you're not just a boy anymore.

2001214.name: What's wrong, Loch? All bark and no bite?

2001221.name: Hmph. There's no way I'm training with you.

2001222.name: Dean, get out of my way! I can't aim right!

2001223.name: Dean, I have to admit, you are pretty strong.

2001224.name: You just got in the way. Tomorrow I'll fight by myself.

2001233.name: Knowing you're no match for a god, you still defy me?

2001235.name: ...thinking they can destroy us with their power.

2001236.name: There is nothing left for you to protect.

2001237.name: You should surrender. Humans cannot defeat gods.

2001238.name: Could it be...that you're trying to seal me away?!

2001241.name: Great land of Palmyna, please lend us your power!

2001242.name: Loch is in trouble! I have to--!

2001243.name: Lafdranya, give me the power to protect everyone!

2001244.name: Even if it means relinquishing my own life...

2001245.name: Professor! I will switch to the vanguard!

2001252.name: Don't assume that this is the extent of my power!

2001253.name: Young man! Now's not the time for your chatter!

2001254.name: Lady Edea! Pushing yourself too hard is dangerous!

2001255.name: Loch, save your energy for the last attack!

2001256.name: I will crush the enemy's defense!

2001262.name: Now you'll learn the real meaning of "Absolute Zero"!

2100070.name: Yo ho! I'm counting on ye!

2100170.name: This is a girls' night out?

2100241.name: Nemia, if I win this one...

2100271.name: A lot of us were captured!

2100280.name: We were bound by time once.

2100290.name: Ho ho ho. I remember that.

2100300.name: Maybe I was still bound too?

2100351.name: My gun's toiled for a year!

2100361.name: It's been a year long fight!

2100431.name: I will draw the enemy fire!

2100531.name: Y-Yes! But can I do it?

2100571.name: Stop! I don't want a fight!

2100582.name: I vowed to become the best!

2100631.name: How will you use your power?

2100652.name: I'll show you my real power!

2100662.name: I won't go easy on you.

2100672.name: I can hear this world's cry!

2100832.name: I wanna have a go at it...

2100862.name: It was born from the fallen.

2100871.name: Uh, why am I with this man?

2100882.name: Tsk, I'm the one put off!

2100883.name: I'll beat you up after this!

2100891.name: Which of us is the cutest?

2100922.name: So many ideas to work with!

2100962.name: I want to believe in Sodis.

2100992.name: My duty is to slay traitors!

2101012.name: I won't let you slay humans!

2101033.name: Looks like fun! I'll go too!

2101042.name: I want to shield my friends.

2101053.name: I see. Alyut is after me...

2101131.name: Ho ho ho. Someone spar me!

2101142.name: All right, let's go all out!

2101151.name: Not too shabby for an idiot!

2101152.name: Moron! Take it a bit easier!

2101182.name: I'd like to duel Lord Oboro.

2101252.name: If so, I shall judge you.

2101262.name: I can tear down any wall.

2101266.name: Fear the might of my blade.

2101303.name: Aid the poor, bash the rich!

2101305.name: I won't let my mark escape!

2101313.name: Watch, I can even do this!

2101321.name: Ouch! Don't hit me so hard.

2101322.name: Show me how you use Items!

2101325.name: Don't muff me! Now I'm mad!

2101331.name: Must I deal with this trash?

2101333.name: What a useless hunk of junk.

2101334.name: I said I'd help. Thank me.

2101345.name: Not bad, but I was better.

2101382.name: Did you see Sodis? I won!

2101410.name: Should I hit or stomp you?

2101431.name: Show me more of your pain.

2101554.name: I will quell the sea's fury.

2101606.name: Well, well... Who knew humans could come this far?
